OL,3,CAsian family 'targeted' in Hartlepool
OL,4,Cdisorder will now leave the town
OL,6,FGregg Easteal spoke to some of those
OL,7,Faffected by disorder in Hartlepool.
OL,9,FAn Asian family are planning on
OL,10,Ffleeing their home after having their
OL,11,Fwindows smashed in what they believe
OL,12,Fwas a targeted attack during riots in
OL,13,FHartlepool.
OL,15,FSpeaking anonymously to ITV Tyne Tees,
OL,16,Fone of the family members living in
OL,17,Fthe property said their curtains were
OL,18,Fripped out and their windows were
OL,19,Fsmashed "for no reason".
