OL,3,CAsian family 'targeted' in Hartlepool
OL,4,Cdisorder will now leave the town
OL,6,FHe said they were left "terrified"
OL,7,Fafter the incident which saw four
OL,8,Fpeople remain inside his house for
OL,9,Faround 20 to 30 minutes.
OL,11,FIt happened as unrest broke out in the
OL,12,Ftown on Wednesday (31 July) evening.
OL,13,FIt marked the second night of disorder
OL,14,Fin locations across the UK following
OL,15,Fthe mass stabbing of children at a
OL,16,Fdance class in Southport, Merseyside,
OL,17,Fon Monday.
OL,19,FOn Thursday, the man whose family home
OL,20,Fwas reportedly raided told ITV Tyne
OL,21,FTees: "I'm going to move from here."
