OL,3,CAsian family 'targeted' in Hartlepool
OL,4,Cdisorder will now leave the town
OL,6,FRiot police were called to help
OL,7,Fdisperse crowds as pockets of unrest
OL,8,Fbroke out in the town on Wednesday at
OL,9,Fabout 6pm.
OL,11,FOfficers were repeatedly pelted with
OL,12,Fbricks and bottles and a police car
OL,13,Fwas set alight.
OL,15,FSimilar scenes of violence were seen
OL,16,Fin London and Manchester overnight
OL,17,Fwhile a demonstration in Aldershot saw
OL,18,Fa tense stand-off with riot police.
